{
  "stem": "979.3",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was the one thing I made, the first thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the nurse were-- were prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of them was a Greek nurse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was telling me, you go here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll-- I'll-- I'll take care of you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll take care of you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, if an order comes for the gas chambers, you think they'll let you-- me take care of you?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, I've got to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used my mind, I say, to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I say it's better than in the back, that going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, I was recovering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very weak and that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there-- one of the two first weeks was the worst.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So nobody got it from me, because I was-- I was almost recovered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was so weak I couldn't see well and everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It took me another week to really-- and then I had to-- I was forced to play, though.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because once you go there, you play.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, they needed-- the orchestra was getting bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed a double bass.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a double bass in the corner in the room, because they brought instruments from people who left their instruments.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And nobody could play the double bass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So now I'm going backwards in Greece-- sorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's gone already.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
